@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

title Sequence Diagram - React Frontend Application Flow

autonumber

actor User
participant "App.tsx" as App
participant "Home.tsx" as Home
participant "room.ts" as RoomHandler
participant "WebSocket" as WS
participant "Backend Server" as Server
participant "Map.tsx" as Map
participant "Navbar.tsx" as Navbar

== Application Initialization ==

User -> App: Load application
activate App

App -> App: Check URL params for room ID
App -> App: Initialize WebSocket ref
App -> App: Create room handler context
App -> App: Generate unique client ID

== WebSocket Connection Setup ==

App -> WS: Create WebSocket('ws://localhost:8765')
activate WS

App -> RoomHandler: attachRoomSocketHandlers(ws, context)
activate RoomHandler
RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Set up onmessage handler
RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Set up onerror handler
RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Set up onclose handler

WS -> Server: WebSocket connection request
activate Server
Server --> WS: Connection established
WS --> App: onopen event

== Room Creation/Joining Flow ==

alt URL has room parameter
    App -> App: Set roomModeRef to 'join'
    App -> App: Set joinRoomIdRef
    WS -> Server: Send {"action": "join", "room": roomId, "token": "..."}
    Server --> WS: {"type": "joined", "room": roomId}
else User clicks "Create Room"
    App -> Home: Render Home component
    activate Home
    User -> Home: Click "Create New Room"
    Home -> RoomHandler: handleCreateRoom(context)
    RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Set roomModeRef to 'create'
    RoomHandler -> WS: Send {"action": "create", "token": "..."}
    WS -> Server: Forward create message
    Server --> WS: {"type": "room_created", "room": roomId}
else User enters room ID and clicks "Join"
    App -> Home: Render Home component
    User -> Home: Enter room ID and click "Join Room"
    Home -> RoomHandler: handleJoinRoom(context, roomId)
    RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Validate room ID
    RoomHandler -> WS: Send {"action": "join", "room": roomId, "token": "..."}
    WS -> Server: Forward join message
    Server --> WS: {"type": "joined", "room": roomId}
end

WS --> RoomHandler: onmessage: room_created/joined
RoomHandler -> App: setRoomId(roomId)
RoomHandler -> App: setIsRoomConnected(true)
RoomHandler -> App: setIsHost(true/false)
RoomHandler -> App: Update URL with room ID
App -> App: isRoomConnected = true
App -> App: Render Map component instead of Home
deactivate Home

== Game World Generation ==

User -> App: Enter world prompt and submit
App -> App: Validate isHost and prompt length
App -> WS: Send {"action": "create_game", "setting": prompt}
WS -> Server: Forward create_game message
Server -> Server: Generate game description using Gemini AI
Server --> WS: {"type": "game_created", "setting": prompt, "description": "..."}
WS --> RoomHandler: onmessage: game_created
RoomHandler -> App: setGameStatusMessage(description)
RoomHandler -> App: setWorldPrompt('')
RoomHandler -> App: setGameSetting(setting)
App -> App: Format markdown to HTML
App -> App: Display game description

== Character Creation ==

User -> Map: Click "Create randomized character"
Map -> App: onRequestCharacterCreation()
App -> WS: Send {"action": "create_character", "clientId": clientId}
WS -> Server: Forward create_character message
Server -> Server: Generate character JSON using Gemini AI
Server --> WS: {"type": "character_created", "character": {...}}
WS --> RoomHandler: onmessage: character_created
RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Validate clientId matches
RoomHandler -> App: setCharacterCreated(true)
RoomHandler -> App: setHp(character.hp)
RoomHandler -> App: setMaxHp(character.maxHp)
RoomHandler -> App: setAc(character.ac)
RoomHandler -> App: setCharacterPortrait(character.portrait)
RoomHandler -> App: setStats(character.stats)
RoomHandler -> App: setAbilities(character.abilities)
RoomHandler -> App: setInventory(character.inventory)
RoomHandler -> App: setCharDescription(character.charDescription)
RoomHandler -> App: setRace(character.race)
RoomHandler -> App: setTraits(character.traits)
App -> Map: Update character props
Map -> Map: Display character HUD

== Mouse Coordinate Tracking ==

User -> Map: Move mouse (while pressed) on map board
Map -> Map: Check if within map bounds
Map -> Map: Throttle coordinate sending (100ms)
Map -> WS: Send {"clientId": id, "x": x, "y": y, "timestamp": ts}
WS -> Server: Forward mouse coordinates
Server -> Server: Broadcast to all clients in room
Server --> WS: Broadcast coordinates to other clients
WS --> RoomHandler: onmessage: coordinate data
RoomHandler -> RoomHandler: Check if message has clientId, x, y
RoomHandler -> App: setClientCoordinates(update map)
App -> Map: Update clientCoordinates prop
Map -> Map: Convert screen coords to board positions
Map -> Map: Render pieces on board

== Piece Movement (Drag & Drop) ==

User -> Map: Drag own piece to new position
Map -> Map: handleDragEnd(event)
Map -> Map: Check if attack is selected (prevent movement)
Map -> Map: Convert board position to screen coordinates
Map -> WS: Send {"clientId": id, "x": x, "y": y, "timestamp": ts}
WS -> Server: Forward new position
Server -> Server: Broadcast to all clients
Server --> WS: Broadcast coordinates
WS --> RoomHandler: onmessage: coordinate update
RoomHandler -> App: setClientCoordinates(update)
App -> Map: Update board positions
Map -> Map: Render piece at new position

== Attack System ==

User -> Map: Select ability from HUD
Map -> Map: handleAbilitySelect(ability, type)
Map -> Map: setSelectedAbility(ability)
Map -> Map: Calculate range squares
Map -> Map: Highlight range squares on board
Map -> App: setIsAttacking(true)

User -> Map: Click target piece in range
Map -> Map: handlePieceSelect(targetClientId)
Map -> Map: Check if target is in range
Map -> Map: Roll d20 for attack
Map -> Map: Calculate hit/miss
Map -> WS: Send {"type": "attack", "attacker": id, "target": targetId, "damage": dmg, "roll": roll}
WS -> Server: Forward attack message
Map -> Map: Display dice roll result
Map -> Map: Reset selection after 3 seconds
Map -> App: setIsAttacking(false)

== Error Handling ==

alt WebSocket Error
    WS --> RoomHandler: onerror event
    RoomHandler -> App: setErrorMessage("WebSocket Error")
    RoomHandler -> App: setIsRoomConnected(false)
    App -> Home: Render Home component (disconnected)
end

alt Invalid Room/Token
    Server --> WS: {"error": "Room does not exist"}
    WS --> RoomHandler: onmessage: error
    RoomHandler -> App: setErrorMessage("Room does not exist")
    RoomHandler -> App: setIsRoomConnected(false)
    App -> Home: Render Home component
end

== Cleanup ==

User -> App: Close browser/leave page
App -> App: Cleanup timeout
App -> WS: Close WebSocket connection
WS -> Server: Close connection
Server -> Server: Remove client from room
Server -> Server: Delete room if empty

deactivate Server
deactivate WS
deactivate RoomHandler
deactivate App

@enduml


